{"tid":2250542,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"出去比錢黐MON貼，唔係貪你黐得好?","createTime":"2020-10-20T07:32:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T12:40:33.000Z","uid":17951,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"4acb5ac5159b726ec586b45ef3838acd68c485e8","tid":2250542,"uid":17951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:32:54.000Z","msg":"話說岩岩隻apple watch mon貼又起bubble，自問手勢差，費時黐到一顏一忽，所以出去搵人搞。<br />\n求其入左一間問價，問完條友索價$148<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />⋯⋯講到防爆防彈咁濟。信心爆棚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />心諗，啲mon貼都係大陸貨，幾多錢張，心照啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。搵得你都係貪你黐得好同埋好服務。點知跟住落嚟既場面，我自己都R撚曬頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n- 店員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黐完啦，你睇睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Errrrr...有塵係入面wo..仲要係好明顯wo..<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(拎返，繼續黐)44mm係難黐D嫁啦...再拎起張mon貼黐仲可能會多D塵..<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (心諗，關我撚事...)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (拎起張mon貼繼續整，但愈整愈衰) 唉..可能呢張唔要得...<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下?咁點?要我比多$140你黐多次?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (扮冇野，繼續黐..)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(黐第完第二張)OK啦今次，你睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />Errrrr...仲係有塵WO老闆，今次仲要多左好多粒wo...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(開始炆陣，換第三張繼續黐...)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(第三張度錯位，黐衰左。)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(第四張又係度錯位，黐衰左。)<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(態度極差) 其實你隻錶著MON果陣係睇唔到D塵，唔需要咁執著D塵WO。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />....你收得咁既價錢，我緊係信你手勢嫁啦，你自己黐得唔好?你要我自己包底?傻撚左?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我唔撚黐啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你搵第二間<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(心諗:做乜鳩?)<br />\n<br />\n大佬啊，你打開門做生意，收得咁既價錢。而我又比得起錢你去幫我搞，我緊係信你可以achieve到我既要求嫁啦。你自己手勢差，自己廢，就要個客就鳩你...冇撚野下話?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 去隔離果間幾下手勢搞掂，一粒塵都冇。都係收我78蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a2b340b774c633d925320bce7997c6871b8482","tid":2250542,"uid":17951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:33:42.000Z","msg":"岩岩手快快禁錯制...重開"},{"pid":"3e1ad448454002aa286fed1c868ef4440604ddde","tid":2250542,"uid":165956,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"你真係唔識嫁wor<br />\n- 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 店員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會咁用嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a375f04eb0ffe48f48ed514eaa8e10d7b148791e","tid":2250542,"uid":17951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e1ad448454002aa286fed1c868ef4440604ddde","tid":2250542,"uid":165956,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T07:35:34.000Z","msg":"你真係唔識嫁wor<br />\n- 我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n- 店員 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點會咁